feMIB.name: feMIB
feMIB.contactinfo: postal: DKT A/S Fanoevej 6 DK-4060 Kirke Saaby Denmark email: info@dktcomega.com

feATU.name: feATU
feATU.description: Dumps the Address Translation Unit (ATU) Switch table in semi colon format

feUnicastDelete.name: feUnicastDelete
feUnicastDelete.description: Removes a unicast MAC address from the Address Translation Unit (ATU) Switch table.

feMulticastDelete.name: feMulticastDelete
feMulticastDelete.description: Removes a multicast IP address from the Address Translation Unit (ATU) Switch table.

feIGMPSnooping.name: feIGMPSnooping
feIGMPSnooping.description: Starts/stops IGMP snooping, input parameter 0 = stops IGMP snooping, 1 = starts IGMP snooping. Per Default IGMP snooping is enabled, but has to be configured per port

feVTU.name: feVTU
feVTU.description: Dumps the VLAN Table Unit (VTU) Switch table in semi colon format

feVLANCreate.name: feVLANCreate
feVLANCreate.description: Creates a VLAN, input parameters are: VID:WAN:LAN1:LAN2:LAN3:LAN4:CPU:NRL-ENABLE

feVLANDelete.name: feVLANDelete
feVLANDelete.description: Deletes a VLAN, input parameter is VLAN VID: 0 - 4095

feClearVTU.name: feClearVTU
feClearVTU.description: Clears the VLAN Table Unit (VTU) Switch table, input parameter 1 = clear VTU table

feDumpPIRLBuckets.name: feDumpPIRLBuckets
feDumpPIRLBuckets.description: Dumps a list of the active buckets.

feDisablePIRLBucket.name: feDisablePIRLBucket
feDisablePIRLBucket.description: Disables an already defined Port Ingress Rate Limitation (PIRL) bucket, input parameter bucket 0 - 11.

feVLANProviderMode.name: feVLANProviderMode
feVLANProviderMode.description: Enable/disable VLAN provider mode, input parameter 0 = disable VLAN provider mode, 1 = enable VLAN provider mode. Per Default VLAN provider mode is disabled. NOTE: Provider VLAN ID should be setup in port default VID for the originating port.

feCPUPortAutoNegotiation.name: feCPUPortAutoNegotiation
feCPUPortAutoNegotiation.description: Enables/disables auto negotiation on the port. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortSpeedMode.name: feCPUPortSpeedMode
feCPUPortSpeedMode.description: Sets/gets the speed and duplex mode on the port. Input parameters are: 100FD|100HD|10FD|10HD|AUTO|FD|HD

feCPUPortLinkStatus.name: feCPUPortLinkStatus
feCPUPortLinkStatus.description: Gets the Link status for the port

feCPUPortFlowControl.name: feCPUPortFlowControl
feCPUPortFlowControl.description: Enables/disables flow control on the port. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortIEEEQoSPriority.name: feCPUPortIEEEQoSPriority
feCPUPortIEEEQoSPriority.description: Enables prioritized frames based on there IEEE priority tags. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortIPQoSPriority.name: feCPUPortIPQoSPriority
feCPUPortIPQoSPriority.description: Enables prioritized frames based on their IP4/IP6 priority fields. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortFramePriorityOverwrite.name: feCPUPortFramePriorityOverwrite
feCPUPortFramePriorityOverwrite.description: Source Address(SA) or Destination Address(DA) Frame Priority Override on an ATU match. XX_FRAME_PRIO_OVERRIDE=0..1.

feCPUPortQueuePriorityOverwrite.name: feCPUPortQueuePriorityOverwrite
feCPUPortQueuePriorityOverwrite.description: Source Address(SA) or Destination Address(SA) Queue Priority Override on an ATU match. XX_QUEUE_PRIO_OVERRIDE=0..1.

feCPUPortQueuePriority.name: feCPUPortQueuePriority
feCPUPortQueuePriority.description: Queue priority, input parameters: PRIO:ENABLE PRIO: 0 - 7 ENABLE: 0 - 1

feCPUPortQoSPortMapRule.name: feCPUPortQoSPortMapRule
feCPUPortQoSPortMapRule.description: Forces queue priority for a port. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortVIDNRLEnable.name: feCPUPortVIDNRLEnable
feCPUPortVIDNRLEnable.description: Enables/disables per port the Non rate limit for VLANs with the NRL bit enabled. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortMap2PIRL.name: feCPUPortMap2PIRL
feCPUPortMap2PIRL.description: Adds/maps the port to a Port Ingress Rate Limitation (PIRL) bucket. Input parameter is PIRL bucket no 0 - 11.

feCPUPortDeletePortMap2PIRL.name: feCPUPortDeletePortMap2PIRL
feCPUPortDeletePortMap2PIRL.description: Deletes the port from a Port Ingress Rate Limitation (PIRL) bucket. Input parameter is PIRL bucket no 0 - 11.

feCPUPortEgressRateLimitation.name: feCPUPortEgressRateLimitation
feCPUPortEgressRateLimitation.description: Sets the egress limitation rate for the port. Input parameter is value in kbps

feCPUPortIngressRateLimitation.name: feCPUPortIngressRateLimitation
feCPUPortIngressRateLimitation.description: Sets a Port Input Rate Limit(PIRL) bucket. Input parameters are: bucket:rate:layer:(DROP|FC)

feCPUPortDefaultVLAN.name: feCPUPortDefaultVLAN
feCPUPortDefaultVLAN.description: Sets the default VLAN ID(VID) for the port. Input parameter is 0 - 4095

feCPUPortForceDefaultVID.name: feCPUPortForceDefaultVID
feCPUPortForceDefaultVID.description: Forces the tagging of VID on all frames on the port. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortVLANPortMode.name: feCPUPortVLANPortMode
feCPUPortVLANPortMode.description: Sets the 802.1Q mode for the ingress port. Mode either 0=disable, 1=fallback, 2=check, 3=secure

feCPUPortBlockAllUnknown.name: feCPUPortBlockAllUnknown
feCPUPortBlockAllUnknown.description: This will make sure that all frames received on the port are blocked, unless they are tagged with the correct VID.

feCPUPortIGMPSnooping.name: feCPUPortIGMPSnooping
feCPUPortIGMPSnooping.description: Enables/disables IGMP snooping. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feCPUPortAddUnicast.name: feCPUPortAddUnicast
feCPUPortAddUnicast.description: Adds the unicast mac address statically to the Address Translation Unit (ATU) Switch table. Input parameter is: aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff

feCPUPortAddMulticast.name: feCPUPortAddMulticast
feCPUPortAddMulticast.description: Adds the IP multicast address statically to the Address Translation Unit (ATU) Switch table. Input parameter is: aaa.bbb.ccc.ddd

feLAN4PortQoSPortMapRule.name: feLAN4PortQoSPortMapRule
feLAN4PortQoSPortMapRule.description: Forces queue priority for a port. Set to 1 for enable and 0 for disable.

feLAN4PortVIDNRLEnable.name: feLAN4PortVIDNRLEnable

feLAN4PortMap2PIRL.name: feLAN4PortMap2PIRL

feLAN4PortDeletePortMap2PIRL.name: feLAN4PortDeletePortMap2PIRL
feLAN4PortDeletePortMap2PIRL.description: Deletes the port from a Port Ingress Rate Limitation (PIRL) bucket. Input parameter is PIRL bucket no 0 - 11.

feLAN4PortEgressRateLimitation.name: feLAN4PortEgressRateLimitation

feLAN4PortIngressRateLimitation.name: feLAN4PortIngressRateLimitation

feLAN4PortDefaultVLAN.name: feLAN4PortDefaultVLAN

feLAN4PortForceDefaultVID.name: feLAN4PortForceDefaultVID

feLAN4PortBlockAllUnknown.name: feLAN4PortBlockAllUnknown

feLAN4PortIGMPSnooping.name: feLAN4PortIGMPSnooping

feLAN4PortAddMulticast.name: feLAN4PortAddMulticast
